      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The senseless Geico caveman ads belong in the dark ages (Consumed, Rob Walker, April 15).</p>
        <p>As the world is ''going green'' these days, give me that sweet, sensible gecko. If, indeed, any character deserves to have a shot at a show of his own, it's the gecko! He gets a green thumbs up here!  June Salzman  Fair Lawn, N.J.</p>
      </block>
